---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout title="Jewish Holidays - Ohr HaTorah" pageTitle="Jewish Holidays & Observances" pageIcon="fas fa-calendar-day">
    <p class="intro-text"><strong>Holiday information and celebration details will be posted as each holiday approaches.</strong></p>

    <p class="description">Throughout the year, we observe and celebrate the biblical holidays including:</p>

    <div class="holidays-grid">
        <div class="holiday-card">
            <div class="holiday-icon">
                <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Shabbat</h3>
            <p>Weekly day of rest and worship</p>
        </div>

        <div class="holiday-card">
            <div class="holiday-icon">
                <i class="fas fa-wine-glass"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Pesach (Passover)</h3>
            <p>Celebrating freedom from Egypt</p>
        </div>

        <div class="holiday-card">
            <div class="holiday-icon">
                <i class="fas fa-wheat-awn"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Shavuot (Pentecost)</h3>
            <p>Festival of the harvest and Torah</p>
        </div>

        <div class="holiday-card">
            <div class="holiday-icon">
                <i class="fas fa-bell"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Rosh Hashanah</h3>
            <p>New Year and time of reflection</p>
        </div>

        <div class="holiday-card">
            <div class="holiday-icon">
                <i class="fas fa-scroll"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Yom Kippur</h3>
            <p>Day of Atonement</p>
        </div>

        <div class="holiday-card">
            <div class="holiday-icon">
                <i class="fas fa-campground"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Sukkot</h3>
            <p>Festival of Tabernacles</p>
        </div>

        <div class="holiday-card">
            <div class="holiday-icon">
                <i class="fas fa-menorah"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Hanukkah</h3>
            <p>Festival of Lights</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="info-box">
        <p>Each holiday brings unique traditions, special services, and community gatherings. Details about timing, services, and how to participate will be shared well in advance.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="contact-box">
        <h4><i class="fas fa-question-circle"></i> For more information about upcoming holidays:</h4>
        <div class="contact-links">
            <a href="tel:+17144061513"><i class="fas fa-phone"></i> (714) 406-1513</a>
            <a href="mailto:OhrHaTorahOC@gmail.com"><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> OhrHaTorahOC@gmail.com</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</PageLayout>

<style>
    .intro-text {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .description {
        text-align: center;
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .holidays-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));
        gap: 20px;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .holiday-card {
        background: var(--gray-100);
        padding: 25px 20px;
        border-radius: 12px;
        text-align: center;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    }

    .holiday-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
        box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .holiday-icon {
        width: 60px;
        height: 60px;
        margin: 0 auto 15px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gold) 0%, var(--gold-dark) 100%);
        border-radius: 50%;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
    }

    .holiday-icon i {
        color: white;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .holiday-card h3 {
        color: var(--primary-blue);
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        margin: 0 0 8px 0;
    }

    .holiday-card p {
        margin: 0;
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .info-box {
        background: var(--gold-light);
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        border-left: 4px solid var(--gold);
        margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .info-box p {
        margin: 0;
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .contact-box {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-blue) 0%, #004080 100%);
        color: white;
        padding: 25px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .contact-box h4 {
        margin: 0 0 15px 0;
    }

    .contact-links {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 20px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .contact-links a {
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        padding: 10px 20px;
        border-radius: 6px;
        transition: background 0.3s ease;
    }

    .contact-links a:hover {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    }
</style>
